        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pianbei/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2495154-2.jpg" alt="北京偏北" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11180553/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11180553/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pianbei/" class=" " title="北京偏北">北京偏北</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11180553">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">这本书让我学习了一遍哲学。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11180553/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
